Use output connectors to push data from CRM Analytics to the remote system. Output connectors can push as part of a data prep output node, and some can also push out unprepared data using sync.

Amazon S3 Output Connection
Azure Data Lake Output Connection (Beta)
Salesforce Output Connection
Snowflake Output Connection
Tableau Online Output Connection

Create a remote connection using the Amazon S3 output connector to write .csv data from CRM Analytics to an Amazon S3 bucket when using Data Prep.
Create a remote connection using the Azure Data Lake output connector to write .csv data from CRM Analytics to Microsoft Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2 when using Data Prep.
Push your prepared dataset data into any Salesforce org from CRM Analytics Salesforce Output connector and Data Prep.
Create a remote connection using the Snowflake output connector to write data from CRM Analytics to a Snowflake table.
Push your prepared data from CRM Analytics into Tableau Online with the Tableau Online Output connector and Data Prep recipes.
